PROGRAM TESTING /30 points

    (3) grep STATUS test*.log
        Are all exit status 0 for test a-e, and 1 for testf*?

    (3) Are all the test*err 0 length files (nothing in them),
        except test f for errors, and test f has proper error
        messages.

    (3) Correct output for test suite (a).

    (3) Correct output for test suite (b).

    (3) Test suite (c) - multiple input files merged to stdout.

    (3) Test suite (d) - did stdin (input2) come between input1, 3,
        where the filename "-" was stdin?

    (3) Test suite (e) - line lengths 10 and 80 respectively.

    (3) Test suite (f1) usage error message

    (3) Test suite (f2) did run input1.dat

    (3) All test runs ran to completion and none caused main
        to fail on an exception.

total testing points=
min 0, max 30

